Instead of writing:

Ex : int time = 20;
     if (time < 18) {
       System.out.println("Good day.");
     } else {
       System.out.println("Good evening.");
     }

You can simply write:

Ex : int time = 20;
     String result = (time < 18) ? "Good day." : "Good evening.";
     System.out.println(result);